---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../../components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Why I Built This Website">
  <Navigation />

  <main id="main-content" class="flex-1 max-w-[68ch] mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-24 flex flex-col gap-12 font-sans">
    
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <header class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div class="flex gap-2 text-xs text-[#71717A] font-mono">
        <span>Essay</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>July 2026</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-medium text-[#FAFAFA] tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Why I Built This Website
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] italic">
        "I don't write because I know. I write because it helps me understand."
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Article Content -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 text-[#FAFAFA] text-base leading-[1.7] tracking-tight font-normal">
      <p>
        In an era of hosted platforms and algorithmic feeds, the personal site remains one of the last independent zones on the web.
        Many developers view portfolios as static advertisements for recruitment.
        I chose to build this website as a personal publication: a clean space for notes, failures, and lessons.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        I decided to reject trendy animations, heavy UI libraries, and glowing decorations.
        The design is built entirely on typographic discipline, zinc tones, and constrained visual width limits.
        This restraint forces focus back onto content and conceptual clarity.
      </p>

      <p>
        A website should not feel like a resume.
        It should reflect the habits and thinking of the builder behind the screen.
        This portal serves as an archive of my technical journey, built to last and persist over time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Article Footer -->
    <footer class="flex flex-col gap-8 border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.06)] pt-12 mt-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-sm">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h4 class="text-xs text-[#71717A] uppercase tracking-wider font-medium">Further Reading</h4>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <li>
              <a href="/writing/why-i-write-in-public" class="text-[#2563EB] hover:underline">
                Why I Write in Public
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
